{"meta":{"title":"Portland Transporation System Plan","slug":"portland-transportation-system-plan","site":"http://pbot-tsp.surge.sh","date":"2017.05.20","description":"<p>Design &amp; Development of pub­lic pol­icy &amp; <span class=\"small-caps\">GIS</span> data pre­sent­ing the City of Portlands plans for 20 years of pub­lic works de­vel­op­ment. The pro­ject has a back end that gen­er­ates search­able, per­for­mant web con­tent from canon­i­cal&nbsp;.docx ﬁles, as well as pre­sent­ing an ap­pli­ca­tion for ex­plor­ing <span class=\"small-caps\">GIS</span> data.</p>\n","collection":"projects","timestamp":1495263600000},"content":"<p>\n    <figure class=\"figure\">\n      <picture>\n        <img class=\"figure-image lazyload\" src=\"https://photos.smugmug.com/Projects/Transporation-service-plan/i-FDz7Dm7/0/06d8752b/180x180/home-X5.png\" data-optimumx=\"1.6\" data-src=\"https://photos.smugmug.com/Projects/Transporation-service-plan/i-FDz7Dm7/0/06d8752b/{width}x5000/home-X5.png\" data-sizes=\"auto\" alt=\"home\">\n      </picture>\n    </figure>\n  </p>\n<p>• Introduce pro­ject, pub­lic money and ac­count­abil­ity, what for and why.\n• Key re­quire­ments around Section 508 and <span class=\"small-caps\">WCAAG</span> <span class=\"small-caps\">AA</span>, the Library com­puter.\n• Map / Text View etc.</p>\n<p>\n    <figure class=\"figure\">\n      <picture>\n        <img class=\"figure-image lazyload\" src=\"https://photos.smugmug.com/Projects/Transporation-service-plan/i-wtLbM6q/0/e06f6dea/180x180/txt-X4.png\" data-optimumx=\"1.6\" data-src=\"https://photos.smugmug.com/Projects/Transporation-service-plan/i-wtLbM6q/0/e06f6dea/{width}x5000/txt-X4.png\" data-sizes=\"auto\" alt=\"txt\">\n      </picture>\n    </figure>\n  </p>\n<p>• Text only view, parsed to <span class=\"small-caps\">HTML</span> from le­gal DocX ﬁles.</p>\n<p>\n    <figure class=\"figure\">\n      <picture>\n        <img class=\"figure-image lazyload\" src=\"https://photos.smugmug.com/Projects/Transporation-service-plan/i-JB6728d/0/44ff0340/180x180/index-XL.gif\" data-optimumx=\"1.6\" data-src=\"https://photos.smugmug.com/Projects/Transporation-service-plan/i-JB6728d/0/44ff0340/{width}x5000/index-XL.gif\" data-sizes=\"auto\" alt=\"index\">\n      </picture>\n    </figure>\n  </p>\n<p>Table of con­tents gen­er­ated from the head­ing tags, ac­ces­si­ble through the in­dex. Scroll to an­i­ma­tions keep the user from get­ting lost.</p>\n<p>\n    <figure class=\"figure\">\n      <picture>\n        <img class=\"figure-image lazyload\" src=\"https://photos.smugmug.com/Projects/Transporation-service-plan/i-6xkt8ZR/0/866a11d6/180x180/search-XL.gif\" data-optimumx=\"1.6\" data-src=\"https://photos.smugmug.com/Projects/Transporation-service-plan/i-6xkt8ZR/0/866a11d6/{width}x5000/search-XL.gif\" data-sizes=\"auto\" alt=\"search\">\n      </picture>\n    </figure>\n  </p>\n<p>The com­plete text is search­able, al­low­ing for quick lo­ca­tion of  in­for­ma­tion by lo­ca­tion or type.</p>\n<p>\n    <figure class=\"figure\">\n      <picture>\n        <img class=\"figure-image lazyload\" src=\"https://photos.smugmug.com/Projects/Transporation-service-plan/i-WDDb2MV/0/f418990b/180x180/layers-X5.png\" data-optimumx=\"1.6\" data-src=\"https://photos.smugmug.com/Projects/Transporation-service-plan/i-WDDb2MV/0/f418990b/{width}x5000/layers-X5.png\" data-sizes=\"auto\" alt=\"layers\">\n      </picture>\n    </figure>\n  </p>\n<p>Canonical data lives in the cities ex­ist­ing <span class=\"small-caps\">GIS</span>, hosted and ex­posed via ArcGIS on­line and con­sumed by Leaﬂet.</p>\n<p>\n    <figure class=\"figure\">\n      <picture>\n        <img class=\"figure-image lazyload\" src=\"https://photos.smugmug.com/Projects/Transporation-service-plan/i-X4MQVL2/0/5ff57824/180x180/draw-X5.png\" data-optimumx=\"1.6\" data-src=\"https://photos.smugmug.com/Projects/Transporation-service-plan/i-X4MQVL2/0/5ff57824/{width}x5000/draw-X5.png\" data-sizes=\"auto\" alt=\"draw\">\n      </picture>\n    </figure>\n  </p>\n<p>Web-speciﬁc car­tog­ra­phy and ren­der­ing sup­port in leaﬂet …</p>\n<p>\n    <figure class=\"figure\">\n      <picture>\n        <img class=\"figure-image lazyload\" src=\"https://photos.smugmug.com/Projects/Transporation-service-plan/i-z3tjSrh/0/5aa8532d/180x180/popup-X5.png\" data-optimumx=\"1.6\" data-src=\"https://photos.smugmug.com/Projects/Transporation-service-plan/i-z3tjSrh/0/5aa8532d/{width}x5000/popup-X5.png\" data-sizes=\"auto\" alt=\"popup\">\n      </picture>\n    </figure>\n  </p>\n<p>Exploration of fea­tures ex­posed via popup.</p>\n<p>\n    <figure class=\"figure\">\n      <picture>\n        <img class=\"figure-image lazyload\" src=\"https://photos.smugmug.com/Projects/Transporation-service-plan/i-2ZnZVsk/0/a06a6e02/180x180/linking-XL.gif\" data-optimumx=\"1.6\" data-src=\"https://photos.smugmug.com/Projects/Transporation-service-plan/i-2ZnZVsk/0/a06a6e02/{width}x5000/linking-XL.gif\" data-sizes=\"auto\" alt=\"linking\">\n      </picture>\n    </figure>\n  </p>\n<p>Connection be­tween data in pop­ups, con­nect­ing to rel­e­vant sec­tion in the text.</p>\n"}